Sentencas: A three-dimensional (3D) computational fluid dynamics (CFDs) electrochemical model has been created to model high-temperature electrolysis stack performance and steam electrolysis in the Idaho National Laboratory (INL) Integrated Lab Scale (ILS) experiment.
Titulo: 3D CFD model of a multi-cell high-temperature electrolysis stack

Sentencas: The model is made of 60 planar cells stacked on top of each other operated as solid oxide electrolysis cells (SOECs).
Titulo: 3D CFD model of a multi-cell high-temperature electrolysis stack

Sentencas: Details of the model geometry are specific to a stack that was fabricated by Ceramatec, Inc.
Titulo: 3D CFD model of a multi-cell high-temperature electrolysis stack
